name: 'The Swashbuckling Adventures of Terry the Testicle.' Comic book by Quim.
description:
Ahoy mateys! It's all hands on deck as we join Terry the testicle in part one of his swashbuckling adventure! Once Terry has escaped from his scrotal home upon a pirate ship, he is free to pursue his life-long dream: to travel to London and meet his idol- Elton John!
This wholly nonsensical tale combines some light hearted fun making, with a joyful exploration of just a couple of London's rich music scenes. So, follow Terry through the highs and the lows as he adventures across the seas and the city, making friends and stopping at various concerts along the way!

32 Page, full colour comic book. First edition.

Excerpts from all Quim's books can be viewed at: www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.529374137134791.1073741829.248974671841407&type=3

'Firm Turd - The Burning' Comic book by Quim.

"As prequel to the 'Firm Turd' detective series, this book demonstrates the making of our hapless hero. Once upon a time, 'Turd was a high-flying Private Detective commissioned by the Police Department. He had a beautiful wife, a faithful pal and of course his steadfast sidekick, Milo the dog. Join Firm Turd as he recounts that night, the night that changed everything, forever.“

24 Page, full colour comic book. First Edition, limited run. Numbered & sealed.

'The Rise and Fall of Keth the Manosaur - Part One' Comic book, by Quim.

“This timeless two part classic of emotional trials and tribulations follows the tragic tale of Keth, a T-Rex born with human arms. Out-cast from the pack, Keth seeks pastures new and travels to the big city in hopes of launching a successful acting career, however not all goes as well as Keth had hoped...“

32 Page, full colour comic book. First Edition, limited run. Numbered & sealed.
